Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:18.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（“恋爱发自真心”）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不行啦  果然还是会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益子老师  不是跟你强调过进房间之前要敲门的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉野屋老师你没听到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么见不得人的书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许看哦  绝对不许打开抽屉偷看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让人在意啊…
